nas-overcapacity-non-issue-just-2009?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争：美国制裁俄罗斯浪潮瞄准中国企业</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/russia-central-asia/article/3261102/ukraine-war-us-takes-aim-chinese-firms-wave-sanctions-targeting-russia?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>数百家实体受到这一大范围举措的打击，其中包括 20 家总部位于中国大陆和香港的公司。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/russia-central-asia/article/3261102/ukraine-war-us-takes-aim-chinese-firms-wave-sanctions-targeting-russia?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国在墨西哥的工厂如履薄冰，习近平与拜登的会谈以及小型电动汽车的意外冲击：7篇有关中美关系的文章</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260915/chinese-factories-mexico-thin-ice-xi-biden-talks-and-surprise-tiny-ev-hit-7-reads-about-us-china?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>陷入困境的美中关系、人权冲击以及陷入大麻烦的学生：这些是南华早报驻海外记者自 2024 年 4 月以来的焦点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3260915/chinese-factories-mexico-thin-ice-xi-biden-talks-and-surprise-tiny-ev-hit-7-reads-about-us-china?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>皮尤研究中心最新调查显示，越来越多的美国人将中国视为敌人</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261098/more-americans-view-china-enemy-new-pew-survey-shows?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>五分之四的受访者表示对中国大陆持负面看法，与去年大致相同。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:01:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3261098/more-americans-view-china-enemy-new-pew-survey-shows?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国的恐龙足迹暗示着巨型猛禽，这与侏罗纪公园的描述相悖</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3261074/dinosaur-footprints-china-hint-giant-raptors-defy-jurassic-park-depictions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>福建省的脚印化石指向了一种新型恐龙，它是已知最大的猛禽之一，比大片中出现的人类大小的“攻击性猎人”要大得多。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3261074/dinosaur-footprints-china-hint-giant-raptors-defy-jurassic-park-depictions?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国将新疆沙漠水稻种植周期缩短一半 开辟粮食安全新战线</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260942/china-halves-rice-growing-cycle-deserts-xinjiang-opening-new-front-food-security-drive?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>科学家们在中国新疆地区的严酷沙漠中成功种植水稻，时间比传统耕作方法缩短了一半，这是中国确保粮食安全的重要一步。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3260942/china-halves-rice-growing-cycle-deserts-xinjiang-opening-new-front-food-security-drive?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷外长承诺访华期间保持“对华友好”政策不变，旨在稳定紧张关系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3261061/argentinas-foreign-minister-pledges-unchanged-china-friendly-policy-during-visit-aimed-steadying?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>戴安娜·蒙迪诺代表团是自去年中国倾向西方的政府上台以来首次对中国进行正式访问。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:30:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3261061/argentinas-foreign-minister-pledges-unchanged-china-friendly-policy-during-visit-aimed-steadying?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国如何制定国际深海矿产开采标准</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3261017/how-us-can-set-standards-international-deep-sea-mineral-mining?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在争夺国际水域关键矿产方面，美国远远落后于中国等其他国家。通过加入联合国海洋法公约，华盛顿可以制定海底矿物勘探的规则。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 11:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/world-opinion/article/3261017/how-us-can-set-standards-international-deep-sea-mineral-mining?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉与百度就中国地图达成合作，无论首席执行官埃隆·马斯克是否愿意</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3261079/tesla-seals-deal-baidu-china-maps-whether-ceo-elon-musk-wants-them-or-not?utm_source=rs